Package: foretell
Type: Package
Title: Projecting Customer Retention Based on Fader and Hardie Probability Models
Version: 0.3
Author: Srihari Jaganathan
Maintainer: Srihari Jaganathan <sriharitn@gmail.com>
Description: Project Customer Retention based on Beta Geometric, Beta Discrete Weibull and Latent Class 
    Discrete Weibull Models.This package is based on Fader and Hardie (2007) 
    <doi:10.1002/dir.20074> and Fader and Hardie et al. (2018) <doi:10.1016/j.intmar.2018.01.002>.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.1)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: stats,nloptr,pracma,Matrix,MASS,numDeriv
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
